### **GDPR Compliance Notice**

This software may process personal data. By using or distributing this software, you agree to the terms of this **Privacy Policy** and **Terms of Service**, which include compliance with **Greek GDPR regulations**.

**Data Controller**: [Your Company Name]

**Purpose**: The software may collect and process personal data for authentication, profile management, and user interaction. All data processing activities will be carried out in compliance with the applicable data protection laws.

**Data Protection Rights**:
- **Right to Access**: You have the right to request access to your personal data.
- **Right to Rectification**: You can correct any inaccuracies in your personal data.
- **Right to Erasure**: You can request the deletion of your personal data in accordance with applicable laws.
- **Right to Restrict Processing**: You can request the restriction of the processing of your personal data under certain circumstances.
- **Right to Data Portability**: You may request your personal data in a machine-readable format.
- **Right to Object**: You can object to the processing of your personal data under certain circumstances.

**Data Retention**: Personal data will be retained only for as long as necessary for the purposes outlined in the Privacy Policy and as required by applicable law.

**Security**: We implement appropriate technical and organizational measures to ensure the security and confidentiality of personal data.

**Data Transfers**: If personal data is transferred outside the European Economic Area (EEA), it will be done in accordance with GDPR provisions and appropriate safeguards.

For more detailed information, please refer to our **Privacy Policy** and **Terms of Service**.
